      "@type": "Question",
      "name": "What is the accounting equation?",
      "acceptedAnswer": {
        "@type": "Answer",
        "text": "The fundamental accounting equation is: Assets = Liabilities + Shareholders' Equity. A balance sheet must always balance according to this formula."
